<br>
Here's some of my disciplines I'd give mages/casters:<br>
<br>
Meditative State - Gives equivilent of Clarity for 3 minutes, stacks with all other mana regen spells/buffs/songs.  Recycle time of 30 minutes.<br>
<br>
SpeedCasting - 10 seconds during which all spells have casting time and recast time cut in half.  Recycle time of 1 hour.<br>
<br>
Specialize - 40 seconds of successful specialization checks.  Recycle time 30 minutes.<br>
<br>
Evoker - The next evocation dmg spell you cast in the next 60 seconds will be a critical hit.<br>
<br>
Conjurer - The next conjuration dmg spell you cast in the next 60 seconds will be a critical hit.<br>
<br>
<br>
Anybody have any other ideas for caster or Magician specific disciplines?  The idea of disciplines is something that you automatically get once reaching a certain high level, not something you have to do aaxp for.  All melee have em, casters don't.<br>
<br>
- Maige<br>
